data.description: Buyer Potential to assume Seller's VA loan at 4%. This desert gem offers the perfect blend of tranquility and modern living spaces. Open floor plan, 3,318 Sqft, 4Bds, 4 Baths, plus separate entrance to office/den. Kitchen is Chef's Dream with modern appliances, working island & prep sink, wine fridge, built in wine rack, large breakfast bar, double dining areas. Great room with gas fireplace, walk out covered patio and stunning backyard Mountain Views. Main living concrete floors, tray ceilings. Large Master Bedroom plus ensuite bathroom, soaking tub, separate shower, large w/in closet, built in cabinets. 2nd and 3rd Bedrooms share Jack n Jill Bathroom. 4th Bedroom/Guest Suite w/bath. 3 Car Garage. Serene, gated neighborhood. City water, gas. Close to I-10 corridor.
